Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31), libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.24.0), libx11-6, libxcomposite1, libxcursor1, libxdamage1, libxext6, libxfixes3, libxi6, libxrandr2, libxrender1, libxss1, libxtst6, libnss3, libcups2, libasound2, libpulse0, libdrm2, libxcb-dri3-0, libxkbcommon0, libatspi2.0-0, libxshmfence1, libxcb1, libxrandr2, libxcomposite1, libxcursor1, libxdamage1, libxext6, libxfixes3, libxi6, libxrender1, libxss1, libxtst6, libnss3, libcups2, libasound2, libpulse0, libdrm2, libxcb-dri3-0, libxkbcommon0, libatspi2.0-0, libxshmfence1, python3-venv, python3-pip, libusb-1.0-0
Maintainer: KioskApp Team <team@kioskapp.com>
Description: Kiosk App with automatic printer and QR scanner detection
 A Flutter-based kiosk application for parking management
 with automatic thermal printer detection via serial port
 and QR scanner detection via USB.
 
 Features:
 - Automatic thermal printer detection (serial port)
 - Automatic QR scanner detection (USB HID)
 - QR code discount system (format: -20, -5, etc.)
 - ESC/POS printing with reduced QR codes
 - Systemd services for printer-agent and qr-scanner-agent
 - Udev rules for automatic device permissions
 - Plug & play installation - just connect hardware and it works!
